# tsx interaction:

    -> set cache data without private key with customer data
    -> set timeout to delete cache data (5 min = 600_000 milliseconds)
    -> send 2fa message to customer
    -> if ok => get private key by cached data and sign transaction
    -> send notif to customer telegram via <getTransactionInfo> method
    -> if not => remove cache data.

